title: Anne Winters
description:
The beautiful, multi-talented actress with the chic Gram, Anne (pronounced “Annie”) Winters, chats it up with Lala today about Netflix’s “13 Reasons Why,” “The Orville” (on Hulu), acting, influencers, and leaving home at the tender age of 17 to pursue her Hollywood dream! They talk dress code violations, exiting bad situations, social media, and protective parents, and Anne shares some details on producing the screen adaptation of “The Unraveling of Cassidy Holmes.”
